                    ('A tragic arc involves a character who:', ['Deteriorates or suffers irreversible loss — often due to a fatal flaw or the oppressive power of social forces', 'Refuses to change despite opportunities, maintaining their original flaws throughout', 'Overcomes significant obstacles to achieve personal growth and happiness', 'Serves as the social critic through whom the author voices commentary']),
